'Today’s men are more confident than ever experimenting with different styles. 

'The Great Gatsby look follows last year’s Mad Men 1950s look, showing that for men retro hair remains firmly in fashion.'

High-street fashion has also been benefiting from the Great Gatsby effect with the likes of Debenhams seeing sales of vintage-inspired items soar by up to 266 per cent.

